RT marc | wolovim.eth 🐼
new post ⚡
an upgrade to real-time event subscriptions using web3py:

EF Python Team: ✨ web3py v7.7.0 released! ✨
in addition to performance improvements and bug fixes, two new features of note: 
1️⃣ a shiny new subscription manager
2️⃣ a contract event `topic` property to make log filtering easier
➡️ event subscriptions explained: https://snakecharmers.ethereum.org/subscriptions/
